appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
More goodness incoming. You can now filter your class list based on class type and/or class location. If your gym runs product pre-orders, you will also now see those on your homepage to easily jump over to the landing page to purchase it.

We also fixed a variety of small bugs like Appointments not using the 24-hour time format when you have that preference set and some URLs in workouts weren’t showing as clickable, but those are both a thing of the past.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: A few more bugs squashed and some updates for you. Now when you book appointments, they will now be added to your device calendar just like your classes. We’ve also added a link on any workout scores you’ve logged to see the description of the workout. We updated the class detail screen also to include some important information we left out like the registration and cancellation policy info for each class.
